2021-15-5 最新教程
debian Ubuntu
apt install unzip -y
apt install python3.7 -y
apt install python3-pip -y
wget https://github.com/ovenone/sub_to_mlsub/archive/refs/heads/main.zip
unzip main.zip
cd sub_to_mlsub-main/
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
python3 main.py


centos

yum install unzip -y
yum install python3.7 -y
yum install python3-pip -y
wget https://github.com/ovenone/sub_to_mlsub/archive/refs/heads/main.zip
unzip main.zip
cd sub_to_mlsub-main/
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
python3 main.py


通用后台运行  
nohup python3 -u main.py >>out.log 2>&1 &   有日志输出 会占用空间  
nohup python3 -u main.py >>/dev/NULL 2>&1 &  无日志输出  不占用空间

结束后台进程 
ps -ef|grep main.py  查看python3 main.py进程的ID号   
kill -9  15656(对应的id号)
